age from 8 km to 15 km, never increasing by more than 10% per week. We'll continue to run at a comfortable, conversational pace, making running a natural part of your daily life. The final week will include a special 21km validation run to celebrate your progress!","stage_id":"base","stage_name":"Aerobic Base Building & Continuous Running","target_distance_km_hight":15,"target_distance_km_low":8,"target_pace":"Comfortable conversational pace (aiming for sustainable effort)","training_focus":"Gradual mileage increase, continuous running, aerobic endurance, consistency, long runs","week_end":13,"week_start":5}],"updated_at":"2026-02-16T01:53:43.706912+00:00"},"success":true}

