{"data":{"created_at":"2026-01-22T01:24:29.537000+00:00","extension_info":null,"id":"rBZfNmdpH4ZnK8oya6f2","is_beginner":true,"main_race_id":"5r1suCOc2dsiFwyBk4BO","race_history":null,"target_evaluate":"Your current ability at 42km with a 7:00/km pace indicates a strong foundation for endurance. The target pace of 5:41/km for 42km is ambitious but achievable with consistent, progressive training. This plan focuses on building a solid aerobic base safely.","tier":"tier_3","total_weeks":13,"training_hightlight":"This 13-week plan is designed specifically for beginners aiming for a 42km race, focusing on safe and sustainable progress. We'll start with a gentle run-walk approach to build habits and prevent injury, gradually transitioning to continuous running. The emphasis is on enjoying the process, listening to your body, and steadily increasing your endurance. We'll celebrate your progress with a validation run at the end of the base period, confirming your readiness for future challenges.","training_plan_name":"Marathon Foundation Builder: 13-Week Journey","training_stage_discription":[{"post_race_recovery":null,"stage_description":"This initial phase is all about gently introducing your body to running through a run-walk strategy. We'll focus on establishing a consistent exercise routine and preventing injuries. Expect weekly mileage to be between 3-6 km, with a focus on comfortable, easy efforts.","stage_id":"conversion","stage_name":"Gentle Start: Conversion to Running","target_distance_km_hight":6,"target_distance_km_low":3,"target_pace":"Easy conversational pace (run segments)","training_focus":"Run-walk intervals, habit formation, injury prevention, active recovery","week_end":4,"week_start":1},{"post_race_recovery":null,"stage_description":"Now that you've built a foundation, we'll gradually transition from run-walk to continuous running, steadily increasing your weekly mileage. The goal is to make running a natural part of your life and build your aerobic endurance. Weekly mileage will range from 8-15 km, focusing on sustained, comfortable efforts. The final week includes a 42km validation run to celebrate your progress!","stage_id":"base","stage_name":"Aerobic Base Building & Endurance Growth","target_distance_km_hight":15,"target_distance_km_low":8,"target_pace":"Easy conversational pace (continuous running)","training_focus":"Continuous running, gradual mileage increase, long slow runs, building running habit","week_end":13,"week_start":5}],"updated_at":"2026-02-16T01:53:48.828000+00:00"},"success":true}

